videos.description: Texas Tech's Jahmi'us Ramsey splashes a 3-pointer off of the behind-the-back from TJ Holyfield.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One Play (Holyfield's behind-the-back pass sets up Ramsey's triple) 2020/3/7

videos.headline: Holyfield's behind-the-back pass sets up Ramsey's triple

videos.description: Udoka Azubuike avoids defenders in the paint and comes up strong with the two-handed jam.

videos.headline: Azubuike flushes the two-handed slam

videos.description: Texas Tech guard Terrence Shannon Jr. finds his way around Kansas' Ochai Agbaji and throws down a two-handed dunk.

videos.description: Texas Tech forward TJ Holyfield knocks down a 3-pointer from the corner to tie the game at 57-57.

videos.description: Despite a late surge from Texas Tech, No. 1 Kansas manages to hold on for a 66-62 victory over the Red Raiders with help of Marcus Garrett's clutch layup late.
